      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Koppen van personen of bustes, in ronde lijsten, eer of heldendom suggererend; Hellenistisch, Romeins.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
